@Title     = Daily mean

@BeginDescription
@IfMan
For every adjacent sequence t_1, ...,t_n of time steps of the same day, it is

o(t,x) = mean{i(t',x), t_1<t'<=t_n}
@EndifMan
@IfDoc
For every adjacent sequence \begin{math}t_1, ...,t_n\end{math} of time steps of the same day, it is: \\
